    {
      "chinese": "大安溪穿過台灣中部，水源是來自於大霸尖山的大小山脈，溪的兩岸排列著馬達拉溪、雪山溪、荻岡溪、大雪溪、北坑溪、南坑溪，匯入大安溪。",
      "ab": "Lyung Penux hiya ga niya balay ’si gska sku te ss’ka na Taywang. pu’ing uwang nya ga minhbku sku rgyax na Papak Wa’a. hminas sku sesyaw nya ga, niya mbku kya ku gong Mtara, Mrayan, Zipaw, Tmaku, Bling, Tawn muwah msu’un sku Lyung Penux.",
